<title>Cross-Site Scripting</title>
<blurb fontsize="4em">Cross-site scripting attacks...</blurb>
<list fontsize="3.75em">
	<bullet>Exploit the trust a user has for a particular site.</bullet>
</list>
<list fontsize="3.75em">
	<bullet>Generally involve Web sites that display foreign data.</bullet>
</list>
<list fontsize="3.75em">
	<bullet>Inject content of attacker's choosing.</bullet>
</list>
